    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "counselors and hotlines dont pay the bills though. they just give you more things to talk about while the numbers keep getting bigger. it feels like the math just doesn't work anymore. it's like i'm just running in place and the floor is falling away. i'm just so stuck.",
